&lt;p&gt;Many years ago, during my early coding adventures, I developed a concrete beam calculator to assist with structural analysis using &lt;strong&gt;Python&lt;/strong&gt;. Today, I&amp;rsquo;m happy to present its modern reincarnation as a web application, powered by &lt;a href="https://streamlit.io/"&gt;Streamlit&lt;/a&gt;. It could be not perfect, but was very useful for me at the beginning of my structural engineering career.&lt;/p&gt;





